{
  "texts": [
    "The data is collected from diverse open-access programming platforms and meticulously curated.",
    "• BIRD (Li et al, 2023f).",
    "The BIRD dataset consists of 12,751 text-SQL pairs and 95 databases, spanning 37 professional domains.",
    "Its primary objective is to evaluate LLMs' comprehension of database values and the external knowledge linkage between natural language queries and database values.",
    "The dataset is curated using techniques like web scraping and synthetic data generation."
  ]
}